title: Etekcity 10 Port Powered External USB 2.0 Hub with LED Indicator, ABS Plastic Material, Support Windows XP/Vista/7/8& MAC
description: Use all of your USB devices at onceOut of USB ports? With the Etekcity® 10-port USB 2.0 hub, you can make that a thing of the past. This USB hub connects to a single USB port on your computer and provides 10 powered USB ports, allowing you to plug in USB devices such as cameras, cell phones, flash drives, external hard drives, webcams, mice, keyboards, controllers, and much more. The hub’s design keeps cable clutter to a minimum and makes the USB ports easily accessible.Powered High-speed USB 2.0 for fast transfer rates.Not only does this USB hub let you connect up to 10 devices to your computer, but it also includes a power adapter, ensuring that whatever you plug into the hub will work optimally. USB 2.0 offers up to 480Mbps transfer rates, quickly transferring files or media or providing a responsive connection with input peripheral devices.
